node.text:
《Mini buffet set》
From @onandondiners
#Aprilfeasting #familydinner 
Love the laksa lemak, ayam lemak kueh and tart! Kueh not sweet and have coconut taste, tart looks hard but its actually flaky and has buttery filling...wings are a lil soggy but still tasty..soon kueh not bad but too lil filling... overall :7.5/10
.
